title: ADC and SUPPORT MAINS looking for a clash team gold 3+
body:
Hi everyone!

Me and my duo here are looking for a clash team to play with, we are looking for TOP, MID and JUNGLE players that are GOLD 3 OR ABOVE. 

Me and my duo here are a BOTLANE DUO and have been playing together for awhile, and know each others play styles quite well.

We are looking for a competitive lineup, I myself have team experience and we both have played clash before. 

If you want to look us up, here is our op.gg;

http://oce.op.gg/multi/query=dramaticchicken%2Chiimjoey

Here is our Mastery Points (if you want to see our comfort picks and champ pool):

https://championmasterylookup.derpthemeus.com/summoner?summoner=DramaticChicken&region=OCE

https://championmasterylookup.derpthemeus.com/summoner?summoner=Hi+im+joey&region=OCE

Thanks in Advance to anyone who joins!

replies.body: im mid gold level, main top and mid, also have duo jg if needed
